title: I Alone Become A God
description: I Alone Become A God English All Chapter SUMMARY Three years ago, he harvested a spiritual fruit, but was snatched by a Shoushan disciple. Three years later, the Moriyama disciple became the most dazzling genius in the sect, but he discovered that the spirit fruit that was taken away was only one ten thousandth of the chance he had obtained. Since then, he has risen like a comet, opening a fabulous road against the sky!
